quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,"Marka arlada la gilgilo gilgilashadeeda daran (Qiyaamada)."
  99,2,"Oo arladu soo bixiso culeysyadeeda (wixii ku aasnaa),"
  99,3,"Aadmigu yidhaahdo: Maxay leedahay?"
  99,4,"Maalintaas waxay ka warrami akhbaarteeda."
  99,5,"Inuu Rabbigaa u waxyooday darteed."
  99,6,"Maalintaas dadku wuxuu u soo dareeri rac rac si loo tusiyo (jazaha)acmaashooda."
  99,7,"Ee qofkii fala samaan le’eg saxar wuu arki,"
  99,8,"Qofkii falana xumaan le’eg saxar wuu arki."
